  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The originality of the MOCITRAINING study lies in the integration of infant and maternal care
      during the pediatric consultation and the assessment of the impact of this type of care in
      the short and medium term on The MOCITRAINING program could contribute to improving the
      quality of parent-child interactions.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
