  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Each child will be included WITH his biological mother at the first-month visit after
             birth.

          -  Age: 1 month + / - 7 days (child), accompanied by his biological mother

          -  Mother able to read French;

          -  Signed consent letter after complete information of parents about the MOCITRAINING
             study, its principle, advantages and disadvantages.

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Preterm babies.

          -  Children from a twin or multiple pregnancy.

          -  Children with somatic diagnosis explaining the presence of digestive, sleeping or
             interactional disorders.

          -  Refusal to participate after clear information about the study;

          -  Refusal to sign the consent letter;

          -  Refusal to be informed of a diagnostic hypothesis;

          -  Participants not covered by the Social Security system;

          -  Participants incapable of consenting or under legal protection (guardianship or
             curatorship).
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
